174 A.3d 521 GINO S. RAMUNDO, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. RITA RAMUNDO, N/K/A RITA FORCELLATI, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-171 September Term 2017

079349 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004729-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
